title: Tupac Lives! (with Jay Ellis)
itunes:title: Tupac Lives! (with Jay Ellis)
description:
Is Tupac still alive and still dressed like 1996 in Cuba? Langston and his guest Jay Ellis (Insecure on HBO) take a trip through all of Tupac's possible survival tactics and hiding places. Also, they learn about a promising new film producer by the name of Rick Boss.
